de.esoco.lib.event

Class GenericEvent<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.esoco.lib.event.GenericEvent<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Event<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ElementEvent

    public class GenericEvent<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Event<T>
    A generic event class that implements the Event interface. The generic type parameter defines the type of the event source that can be queried with the getSource() method.
